topic.title: Australian Chinese themed and sponsored study
topic.body:
http://127.0.0.1:43111/1AUCvyDuqsDF4EVEgRB2p3v4birGM6EDQp/

For 10 namecoins I will perform this themed study about Australian Chinese, their unique background, the challenge, the opportunity, and the urgent issues that not only face these two people but much of the world.
